org.hibernate.boot.model.relational

Interface MappedTable<T extends MappedColumn>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.hibernate.internal.util.Loggable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DenormalizedMappedTable<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DenormalizedTable, Table

    public interface MappedTable<T extends MappedColumn>
extends Loggable
    Models any mapped "table reference" (e.g. a physical table, an in-lined view, etc).
